  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- as long as they have had some kind of education, whether it's or other material that has been developed of an educational nature, highly developed by the University of Denver in bibliographies, that we are going to have much more of an understanding among young people-- and I think it should be earlier than seventh and eighth grade-- about the differences among people and the ethnic, racial, and religious differences, and that we have to respect-- respect is the word that I want to use-- the differences in people, the--.",
      "word_count": 92
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- the-- we have to learn-- and-- and I always stress this-- that we've got to get rid of the hatred and the prejudice that we have, whether it's against the blacks, the Jews, the Muslims, the Protestants, the Catholics-- always from on the other side of a spectrum.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would do the same, to go to Germany to work on the trials.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of the experience and learning what went on-- learning how, why-- trying to learn why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never could understand why, how a country like Germany, a modern, civilized society of my heritage-- I'm not Jewish, I'm half-German-- could look the other way to the extent that those who knew did.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a society that produced such brilliant writers, composers, and scientists-- Goethe, Kant, Bach, Beethoven, and yes, Hitler's Wagner, Bessel, Roentgen, and Einstein.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel very fortunate to have been able to somehow, some way, been so driven to go there to work as a reporter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was so devastated, you know, to have me go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have learned what happens with the word 'genocide.' And I think that in our high schools, we should pay more attention to education about the past and about the genocide.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
